reviewText: This had three little Christmas cartoons, but only one of them was tom and jerry so that was a bit disappointing since it said it was their night before Christmas.  There was nothing wrong with tape itself and it arrived when it was supposed.  The contents of tape was no fault of seller, just the maker of tape as the 3 cartoons were listed on back.
Easy transaction, quick delivery, great movie. Two thumbs up.

We use to love Tom and Jerry the cartoon as a kids and wanted to came up with an idea for our new Tom and Jerry cartoon in 1988 as school kids !
We could not came up with anything on Tom and Jerry cartoon that was new!
But I still love the cartoon of Tom and Jerry that I watch it everyweek on
Cartoon Network ! It is a joy to watch and bring me back to my childhood of Tom and Jerry !
